{"tid":1558130,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"純討論 休班警棍論","createTime":"2019-09-10T11:00:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T11:04:41.000Z","uid":224058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1b0b22bb191c558202ffdfac51bd3dd1584befa6","tid":1558130,"uid":224058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:00:18.000Z","msg":"現時大家針對一點<br />\n唔肯show pass<br />\n但有警棍就＝狗<br />\n<br />\n如果我地淘寶/市面上買到類似警棍既野<br />\n<br />\n第一時間可能覺得自己好醒，可以破解警棍論<br />\n<br />\n但如果人地狗有number證明戈枝係警棍<br />\n<br />\n而我地拎住一碌棍<br />\n<br />\n又比人告番轉頭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警棍？不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我推薦大家淘寶麵粉棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可用key words 太鼓棍取代<br />\n<br />\n全民太鼓之達人不是夢<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"ccd90ad55890c737168a7e424fb0696a0eba1c63","tid":1558130,"uid":108814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:02:14.000Z","msg":"有春用咩<br />\n狗拿反而有用<br />\n多支棍自慰"},{"pid":"d8df785828b69cc4a67537c5af4a04013bd6a6c9","tid":1558130,"uid":240664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:04:41.000Z","msg":"要攞走支棍"}]}